Revision history for Dancer-Template-Mason2

** denotes an incompatible change

0.05  May 20, 2015

- Allow dhandlers by letting Mason2 decide if the view file exists rather than Dancer - https://github.com/jonswar/perl-dancer-template-mason2/pull/1 (Michael Scoltock)

0.04  May 20, 2012

- convert slashes on Windows - RT #76934 (George Rogers)

0.03  Sep 23, 2011

- in 02-basic.t, touch template so it will be recompiled, and switch to 'has' syntax
- remove t/data from distribution

0.02  Mar 10, 2011

- Use new Mason 2.05 default file extensions (.mc) in documentation and tests

0.01  Feb 21, 2011

- Initial version

